Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway go deep on Robert Mueller wasting taxpayer money on a 2 year investigation that didn't produce any meaningful results and holding a press conference about it, they discuss in depth the drinking and drug schedule that Hunter S. Thompson was on and how Dan wants to recreate it, the guy who set himself on fire in front of the White House today, and the alien aircraft the Navy pilot witnessed.
